{
  "stem": "8892.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he was Draped by Star, but after that I changed the name, Five Star, for my ch-- for five of us, for the children.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I had to come up with the name and keep the Star, so I thought this would be just right.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the girls in there, nobody knew that I am owning already the store, just to watch what's going on, how to sell, and how to order, and all that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my husband still was working for his uncle, so it really helped us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was on like for a year, I was running the store.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And about four, five weeks later, I let the manager know that they're all working for me and I own the store.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were very good to them and they were pleased-- oh, God-- pleased to, you know, that that's happening, and there was no disruption and no interruption.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And business was as usual, and thank God we managed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then two years-- not even two years later, I bought a second store because we expanded.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By that time, my husband stopped his business, you know, the meat business, and he started to learn this business.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my kids were grown already, and they helped us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were transferring merchandise from Lincoln Park to Mt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Clemens and back and forth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then one of the buyers approached me that I should open up in Rochester, that's the upcoming area, and that's where I belong, and for doing customs.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, and I thought I was pretty good, and I knew how to measure and everything was going.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But in Lincoln Park was not much of an opportunity for custom.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
